               <p>I live in <placeName id="t17780715-48-crimeloc230">Three-Tun-alley, Wentworth-street, Petticoat-lane</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t17780715-48-crimeloc230" type="placeName" value="Three-Tun-alley, Wentworth-street, Petticoat-lane"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t17780715-48-crimeloc230" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t17780715-48-off228 t17780715-48-crimeloc230"></join>; on the second of June I went out about three o'clock, and returned at about seven; then I found the back door broke open, and the things mentioned in the indictment gone; the door was bolted on the inside; it is a loose door, a knife had been put in, to push back the bolt; there was the scratches of the knife on the bolt; my wife and children went out with me; I left no one in the house; I have found none of the things again but a gown that was pawned.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17780715-48-person477">
                  Thomas
                   Townsend
               <interp inst="t17780715-48-person477" type="surname" value="Townsend"></interp>
